<li><strong>Diverse University Structure:</strong> Both well-established public universities (Boğaziçi, METU) and modern foundation universities (Koç, Sabancı, Bilkent) offer education in English.</li>



<li><strong>Detailed Application Process:</strong> In addition to basic documents such as high school diploma and transcripts, universities&#8217; own exams (TR-YÖS) or international exams (SAT, TOEFL, IELTS) may be required for application.</li>



