<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-can-apply-to-university-summer-school">Who can apply to university summer school?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In general, the university&#8217;s own students (those who have failed courses, those who want to improve their grades), those who are in the graduation stage and students of other universities with <strong>special student</strong> status can apply.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-16T11:08:47Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-10-16T11:08:48Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/summer-school-programs-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Summer School Programs in Turkey: Opportunities and Application Guide","title":"summer-school-programs-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'summer-school-programs-in-turkey' );
