<li>He takes on critical tasks such as the design of sustainable energy systems, waste management and carbon emission calculations.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Job opportunities:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Environmental impact assessment (EIA) specialist in wind and solar energy companies</li>



<li>Consulting engineer for green energy projects</li>



<li>Carbon emissions management and <strong>climate change expert</strong></li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Especially if you want to take part in large energy projects, you can make a difference by obtaining <strong>international certifications (such as LEED, ISO 14001)</strong>!</p>


