<li><strong>Career Advantage:</strong> Job opportunities are wide in embassies and French companies.</li>



<li><strong>Detailed Information:</strong><a href="https://www.gsu.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Galatasaray University Official Website</a></li>
</ul>



