<li><strong>Career Advantage:</strong> Provides a strong foundation for careers in the public sector and academia.</li>



<li><strong>Detailed Information:</strong><a href="https://www.istanbul.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Istanbul University Official Website</a></li>
</ul>


