<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-for-international-relations-graduates">Career Opportunities for International Relations Graduates</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are a wide variety of career paths for international relations graduates in Turkey and around the world. Here are some of the most popular options:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-diplomacy-and-public-service">1. Diplomacy and Public Service</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You can work as a diplomat in the Ministry of Foreign Affairs.</li>



<li>You can work in embassies and consulates.</li>



<li>You can be a foreign policy analyst or expert in government agencies.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-international-organizations-and-ngos">2. International Organizations and NGOs</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You can take part in organizations such as the United Nations (UN), the European Union (EU) and NATO.</li>



<li>You can work for international non-governmental organizations (NGOs) working in the fields of human rights, environment or global development.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-private-sector-and-media">3. Private Sector and Media</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You can work in international companies in foreign relations, trade or consulting.</li>



<li>You can pursue a career in the media industry as an international journalist, foreign correspondent or political analyst.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-academic-career">4. Academic Career</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You can become an academic by doing master&#8217;s and doctorate.</li>



<li>You can specialize in international politics and security studies at research centers.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-and-grants-for-international-relations-education-in-turkey">Scholarships and Grants for International Relations Education in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many scholarship opportunities for international students in Turkey. Here are the most popular scholarship programs:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Turkey Scholarships:</strong> Undergraduate and graduate programs with full scholarships for foreign students.</li>



<li><strong><strong>TUBITAK Scholarships:</strong> Provides support for students who want to do research.</strong></li>



<li><strong><strong>University Scholarships:</strong> Universities such as METU, Koç and Sabancı offer their own scholarship programs.</strong></li>
</ul>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
