<li><strong>The Department of Industrial Design</strong> is considered one of the best design programs in Turkey and encourages its students to participate in <strong>international competitions</strong>. </li>



<li><strong>Department of Interior Architecture</strong> is a program that stands out with innovative design solutions.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">🔎 <strong>Art and Design Education at ITU:</strong></p>



