Management Programs in Turkey","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/sports-science-and-management-programs-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/sports-science-and-management-programs-in-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/sports-science-and-management-programs-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/sports-science-and-management-programs-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="dreaming-of-a-sports-filled-career">Dreaming of a Sports-Filled Career?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Do you want to make a difference on and off the field, not just watch sports? A sports sciences and management education in Turkey could be for you! </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The sports industry is booming here, with opportunities in everything from soccer to basketball, swimming to athletics. Moreover, Turkey shines in this field with its well-established universities and the opportunities it offers to international students. </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Which universities stand out, how do you apply and what awaits you after graduation? I explain it all in this guide, let&#8217;s get started! </p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-courses-are-there-in-the-department-of-sports-sciences-and-management">What Courses Are There in the Department of Sports Sciences and Management?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports science and management education in Turkey offers a wide range of courses that provide students with both academic and practical knowledge. These courses cover different aspects of sport, giving students a comprehensive perspective.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-basic-scientific-courses">1. Basic Scientific Courses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These lessons are essential for understanding the scientific foundations of sport:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Sports Physiology</strong> &#8211; Studies how the human body works during exercise and how the muscular, circulatory and respiratory systems affect sports performance.</li>



<li><strong>Biomechanics</strong> &#8211; Analyzes the physical principles of human movement and teaches how they can be optimized to improve sports performance.</li>



<li><strong>Science of Exercise and Training</strong> &#8211; Different types of training, performance enhancement strategies and methods of tracking athletes&#8217; progress are taught.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-sport-management-and-organization-courses">2. Sport Management and Organization Courses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The sports industry is not limited to on-field achievements; management and organizational skills are also of great importance. These courses aim to train professionals for sports clubs, federations and organizations:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Sports Management and Marketing</strong> &#8211; Examines how sports organizations are managed, marketing strategies and how sponsorship deals are made.</li>



<li><strong>Sports Law</strong> &#8211; Covers legal processes in the sports industry, player contracts and ethical issues such as doping.</li>



<li><strong>Sports Economics</strong> &#8211; Provides information on the economic aspects of the global and local sports industry, financial management and the financial structures of clubs.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-psychology-and-sociology-lessons">3. Psychology and Sociology Lessons</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Understanding the psychological and sociological dimensions of sport is important for managing the performance of athletes and teams:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Sports Psychology</strong> &#8211; Covers the topics of athlete motivation, stress management and performance psychology.</li>



<li><strong>Sports Sociology</strong> &#8211; Examines the impact of sport on society, fan culture and the role of sport in social change.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-applied-and-elective-courses">4. Applied and Elective Courses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The department also offers many applied courses and elective courses where students can put their theoretical knowledge into practice:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Coaching Education</strong> &#8211; Sports-specific training techniques are taught for students who want to become a professional sports coach.</li>



<li><strong>Sports Nutrition</strong> &#8211; Topics such as how to create nutrition plans for athletes, the effects of diet on performance are covered.</li>



<li><strong>Physical Activity and Health</strong> &#8211; Focuses on the health effects of physical activity, exercise prescriptions and wellness programs.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to this wide range of courses, students can shape their careers by specializing in different areas of the sports industry.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="applied-education-and-internship-opportunities">Applied Education and Internship Opportunities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports science and management education in Turkey is not limited to theoretical knowledge, but also offers students hands-on experiences. Universities provide opportunities for students to:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-internship-programs">1. Internship Programs</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Sports science faculties in Turkey offer their students compulsory or voluntary internship opportunities in sports clubs, federations or private sports facilities.</li>



<li>Particularly in popular sports such as soccer, basketball and volleyball, students can participate in the training process and work with managers.</li>



<li>Internships better prepare students for the world of work and increase their chances of finding a job after graduation.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-field-studies">2. Field Studies</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Universities support students to gain field experience by organizing sports events for them.</li>



<li>Sports science faculties help students develop their management skills by offering them the opportunity to take part in sports organizations.</li>



<li>Some programs encourage students to participate in international sporting events, giving them the chance to observe global sport management and organizations.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-research-and-laboratory-studies">3. Research and Laboratory Studies</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Laboratory studies are carried out in areas such as sports physiology, biomechanics and training science.</li>



<li>Thanks to scientific research such as athlete performance analysis, strength and endurance tests, students have the opportunity to improve themselves in the academic field as well.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-best-universities-providing-sports-sciences-education-in-turkey">The Best Universities Providing Sports Sciences Education in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many universities in Turkey offer sports science and management degrees. Here are some of the best options:</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-hacettepe-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi">1. Hacettepe University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Ankara)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hacettepe University is one of the first universities that comes to mind when it comes to sports science education in Turkey. The faculty stands out with its education approach based on scientific research. The university&#8217;s sports laboratories, biomechanical analysis and conditioning centers offer students a comprehensive education.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Sports physiology, biomechanics, exercise science</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Strong academic staff, laboratory facilities, international collaborations</li>



<li><strong>Residential Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.hacettepe.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.hacettepe.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hacettepe University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-marmara-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-istanbul">2. Marmara University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Istanbul)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Marmara University has one of the most successful faculties in Turkey, especially in sports management and coaching. Its location in the center of Istanbul offers students the chance to take part in major sports organizations and gain field experience.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Sports management, coaching, recreation</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Proximity to Istanbul&#8217;s sports organizations, wide internship opportunities</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.marmara.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.marmara.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marmara University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-ankara-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-ankara"><strong>3. Ankara University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences</strong><em>(Ankara)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara University is home to important academic studies and applied training in the field of sport sciences and management in Turkey. It offers a strong program for students who wish to specialize in sport psychology and movement sciences.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Sports psychology, motor development, movement sciences</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Combination of research-oriented education, psychology and sports science</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://www.sporbilimleri.ankara.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.sporbilimleri.ankara.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ankara University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-gazi-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-ankara">4. Gazi University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Ankara)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Gazi University is one of the well-established centers of sports science education in Turkey. In addition to academic education, it offers students extensive internship and field experience thanks to its proximity to sports organizations.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Areas:</strong> Exercise science, sport management, health and performance</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Cooperation with sports federations, strong research projects</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.gazi.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.gazi.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gazi University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-ege-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-izmir">5. Ege University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Izmir)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ege University is one of the leading universities in the field of sports sciences, offering students hands-on training. The opportunities it offers in the fields of sea sports and recreation differentiate it compared to other universities.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Areas:</strong> Recreation, water sports, sports management</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Sports and recreation opportunities, hands-on training opportunities in the coastal city of Izmir</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.ege.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.ege.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ege University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="6-sakarya-university-faculty-of-sports-sciences-sakarya">6. Sakarya University &#8211; Faculty of Sports Sciences (Sakarya)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sakarya University, which has risen rapidly in the field of sports sciences in recent years, has modern facilities especially in the fields of coaching education and performance analysis. It is an important center especially for students who want to improve themselves in sports technologies and innovative training methods.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Coaching, sport technologies, performance analysis</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> New and modern sports facilities, technology-supported education</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.subu.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.subu.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sakarya University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="7-akdeniz-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-antalya">7. Akdeniz University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Antalya)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Akdeniz University provides a great advantage in the fields of sports management and sports tourism due to its location in Antalya, the capital of tourism. It is an ideal option for those who want to focus on sea sports, nature sports and sports tourism.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.akdeniz.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.akdeniz.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Akdeniz University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Featured Areas:</strong> Sports tourism, extreme sports, sports management</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Advantages:</strong> Access to sports organizations in Antalya, large field work</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-application-process-for-the-department-of-sports-sciences-and-management-in-turkey">The Application Process for the Department of Sports Sciences and Management in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are two different ways to study sports science and management in Turkey:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>YKS (Higher Education Institutions Examination) Placement</strong></li>



<li><strong>International Student Applications (YÖS, SAT etc.)</strong></li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications are usually made between April and July every year. For detailed application processes, you can check the official pages of the universities or get professional support from the <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">roadtostudy.com</a> team.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-for-sports-sciences-and-management-graduates">Career Opportunities for Sports Sciences and Management Graduates</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many career options for graduates of this department. Here are some popular professions:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sports-manager">Sports Manager</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports managers work in sports clubs, federations, private sports organizations and government agencies, managing organizational and strategic processes. They work on issues such as sports event planning, budget management, sponsorship agreements and marketing strategies.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Professional football, basketball, volleyball clubs</li>



<li>Turkish Football Federation, Basketball Federation, Olympic Committees</li>



<li>Sports departments of municipalities</li>



<li>Sports events and organization companies</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Organizational and leadership skills, knowledge of marketing and finance management, knowledge of sports law</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="coach">Coach</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports Science and Management graduates can work as individual or team coaches, managing the physical development of athletes and helping to improve their performance.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Professional sports clubs (soccer, basketball, swimming, volleyball, etc.)</li>



<li>National teams and Olympic athletes</li>



<li>Specialized sports academies and performance centers</li>



<li>Fitness and fitness centers</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Knowledge of sports physiology, ability to create training programs, motivation skills</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sports-psychologist">Sports Psychologist</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports psychologists work to improve athletes&#8217; mental toughness and help them maximize their performance.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Professional sports clubs and national teams</li>



<li>Sports rehabilitation centers</li>



<li>Universities and research centers</li>



<li>Counseling services for individual athletes</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Knowledge of psychology, sports coaching competence, stress management and motivation techniques</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sports-marketing-specialist">Sports Marketing Specialist</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most lucrative fields for Sports Science and Management graduates is sports marketing and brand management. They create sponsorship agreements by promoting sports organizations and clubs.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Sports clubs and organization companies</li>



<li>Digital media and sports agencies</li>



<li>Big sporting events and brands</li>



<li>Sponsorship management departments</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Digital marketing knowledge, sports economics and sponsorship management</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sports-media-and-broadcasting">Sports Media and Broadcasting</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports media covers many areas such as television, digital platforms, radio and social media. Sports science graduates can choose many career paths such as sports journalism, commentary, analysis and content production.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Television channels and digital media platforms</li>



<li>Sports newspapers, magazines and websites</li>



<li>Social media content creation</li>



<li>Media departments of sports organizations</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Effective communication skills, sports knowledge, ability to produce content</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="fitness-and-rehabilitation-specialist">Fitness and Rehabilitation Specialist</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students studying Sports Science and Management can specialize in sports health and fitness and become personal trainers or rehabilitation specialists.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Gyms and individual fitness counseling centers</li>



<li>Health and rehabilitation clinics</li>



<li>Hospitals working on sports injuries</li>



<li>Personal coaching services</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Knowledge of exercise science, knowledge of human anatomy, ability to design individual programs</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-career-and-research-assistant">Academic Career and Research Assistant</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Graduates of the Department of Sports Science and Management can work as lecturers or researchers in universities by making an academic career. They can contribute to the fields of sports technologies and exercise sciences by conducting new research related to sports science.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Fields of work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Universities and academic research centers</li>



<li>Institutes working on sports sciences</li>



<li>Sports technology and innovation laboratories</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Required skills: Research skills, academic writing skills, critical thinking</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As the sports sector is growing rapidly in Turkey, job opportunities in this field are increasing every year.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="sonuç-turkiyede-spor-bilimleri-okumak-size-uygun-mu">


<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">Is Studying Sports Sciences and Management in Turkey Suitable for You?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to pursue a career in the world of sports, studying sports science and management in Turkey can be a great opportunity. You can both get an academically strong education and make a place for yourself in the dynamic sports industry.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Do you think it is attractive to study sports sciences in Turkey? Which city would you like to study in? Share in the comments!</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Contact <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">roadtostudy.com</a> for more information and application support!</p>



