<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-marmara-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-istanbul">2. Marmara University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Istanbul)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Marmara University has one of the most successful faculties in Turkey, especially in sports management and coaching. Its location in the center of Istanbul offers students the chance to take part in major sports organizations and gain field experience.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Sports management, coaching, recreation</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Proximity to Istanbul&#8217;s sports organizations, wide internship opportunities</li>



