<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-ankara-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-ankara"><strong>3. Ankara University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences</strong><em>(Ankara)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ankara University is home to important academic studies and applied training in the field of sport sciences and management in Turkey. It offers a strong program for students who wish to specialize in sport psychology and movement sciences.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Sports psychology, motor development, movement sciences</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> Combination of research-oriented education, psychology and sports science</li>



<li><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://www.sporbilimleri.ankara.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.sporbilimleri.ankara.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ankara University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></li>
</ul>


