<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="6-sakarya-university-faculty-of-sports-sciences-sakarya">6. Sakarya University &#8211; Faculty of Sports Sciences (Sakarya)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sakarya University, which has risen rapidly in the field of sports sciences in recent years, has modern facilities especially in the fields of coaching education and performance analysis. It is an important center especially for students who want to improve themselves in sports technologies and innovative training methods.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Featured Fields:</strong> Coaching, sport technologies, performance analysis</li>



<li><strong>Advantages:</strong> New and modern sports facilities, technology-supported education</li>



