<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="7-akdeniz-universitesi-spor-bilimleri-fakultesi-antalya">7. Akdeniz University &#8211; Faculty of Sport Sciences <em>(Antalya)</em></h3>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Akdeniz University provides a great advantage in the fields of sports management and sports tourism due to its location in Antalya, the capital of tourism. It is an ideal option for those who want to focus on sea sports, nature sports and sports tourism.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Official Website:</strong><a href="https://sporbilimleri.akdeniz.edu.tr/" data-type="link" data-id="https://sporbilimleri.akdeniz.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Akdeniz University Faculty of Sport Sciences</a></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Featured Areas:</strong> Sports tourism, extreme sports, sports management</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Advantages:</strong> Access to sports organizations in Antalya, large field work</p>


